.TH AGENT-HOOK-SESSION-END-CLAUDE 1 "2026-06-30" "agentguard" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
agent-hook-session-end-claude \- Claude-specific session-end maintenance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B agent-hook-session-end-claude
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B agent-hook-session-end-claude
is the Claude-facing session-end entry point. It can name untitled Claude
sessions through
.BR claude-session-name (1)
and runs Claude-specific extension maintenance while preserving AgentGuard's
shared hook response contract.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Claude session-end maintenance completed.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR claude-session-name (1),
.BR agent-hook-session-end (1)
